OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784387896
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter 75 year old found dead
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched in Bolton after the death of
OL,8,Fa 75-year-old man.
OL,10,FA 49-year-old woman has been arrested
OL,11,Fon suspicion of murder.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police were called
OL,14,Fto Ormrod Street in Bolton at around
OL,15,F8am on Friday July 17.
OL,17,FThe man was pronounced dead on the
OL,18,Fscene after being found inside a
OL,19,Fproperty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
