OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784387896
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter 75 year old found dead
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police said
OL,7,Fofficers are 'continuing to pursue
OL,8,Fmultiple lines of enquiry to establish
OL,9,Fthe full circumstances'.
OL,11,FThe victim's next of kin has been
OL,12,Finformed and the family are being
OL,13,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,15,FDetective Inspector Louise Kelly said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
