OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784387896
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter 75 year old found dead
OL,6,F"I would like to express my deepest
OL,7,Fcondolences to the victim's family and
OL,8,Floved ones as they navigate through
OL,9,Fthis loss. They will continue to be
OL,10,Fsupported by our specialist officers
OL,11,Fduring this difficult time."
OL,13,F"It is our priority to obtain some
OL,14,Fanswers regarding the full
OL,15,Fcircumstances of this tragic incident,
OL,16,Fand we are appealing for information
OL,17,Ffrom the public to help us progress
OL,18,Four investigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
