OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784387896
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter 75 year old found dead
OL,6,F"Our Major Incident Team have launched
OL,7,Fa murder investigation and are
OL,8,Fcontinuing to pursue multiple lines of
OL,9,Fenquiry to establish the full
OL,10,Fcircumstances."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
